# Commercial License for Brabus Stories

## Commercial Use Rights

This commercial license grants you the right to use "Brabus Stories" collection for commercial purposes, including but not limited to:

- **Publishing** — Include stories in commercial publications, magazines, anthologies
- **Adaptation** — Create derivative works such as audiobooks, films, games, or other media
- **Distribution** — Sell, license, or distribute the stories commercially
- **Translation** — Create commercial translations in other languages
- **Performance** — Use for commercial readings, podcasts, or performances

## License Terms

### Grant of Rights
Upon payment of the commercial license fee, you are granted a non-exclusive, worldwide license to use the licensed stories for commercial purposes.

### Attribution Requirements
Commercial use must include appropriate attribution:
- **Author:** Brabus
- **Original Source:** EasyProTech LLC
- **Contact:** https://t.me/easyprotech

### Restrictions
- You may not claim authorship of the original stories
- You may not sublicense the stories to third parties without written permission
- Any derivative works must clearly indicate they are based on original stories by Brabus

### License Fees
Commercial licensing fees vary based on:
- **Scope of use** (single story vs. full collection)
- **Distribution scale** (local vs. global)
- **Media format** (print, digital, audio, video)
- **Duration** (one-time vs. ongoing use)

